Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:02.91,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}音も無く迫る闇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.04,0:23:08.32,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}光を灯す為 今こそ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.43,0:23:10.58,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}ぶち壊すFate & Fear
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.71,0:23:14.13,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}生まれ持った衝動で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.24,0:23:20.44,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}全てを掴み獲れ今すぐ ただ…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.79,0:23:24.26,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}真実を手に!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.59,0:00:38.18,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}扣下击断烦恼的扳机
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.33,0:00:42.72,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}毫无用处的自尊在垃圾回收日舍弃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.17,0:00:47.60,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}猎取一切的武士疯狂起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.77,0:00:51.34,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}内燃机频频轰鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.48,0:00:53.65,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}生命仍将延续
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.91,0:00:57.74,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}即使是糜烂的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.54,0:01:02.49,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}在叹息之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.30,0:01:06.49,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}跟随神风
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.60,0:01:08.61,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}向着未知之处前行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.60,0:01:13.82,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}鼎沸的热情与
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.05,0:01:19.17,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}熏染的灵魂勒紧胸口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:23.64,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}如同燃烧的火焰般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.76,0:01:26.09,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}能在此找到自己的容身之地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.19,0:01:29.61,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}雷达之下寻找自己的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.80,0:01:36.03,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}举起钢刃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.18,0:01:44.60,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}纵情呻吟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.83,0:01:51.94,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}继续这不羁的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.49,0:22:17.62,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}燃焦这唯一的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.03,0:22:22.57,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}前进直到血干枯之时
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.67,0:22:32.23,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}远方天空反射过来的光照耀此身
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.61,0:22:35.09,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}消逝散落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.35,0:22:42.13,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}胸中充满激烈的波动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.47,0:22:56.56,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}紧握的手的疼痛谁人能知!
