Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:02.91,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}悄无声息迫近的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.04,0:23:08.32,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}只为点亮光明  现在正是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.43,0:23:10.58,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}毁灭破坏与和平
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.71,0:23:14.13,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}用与生俱来的冲动
